comments: Green (PHI) and Pritchard (BOS) each make clean contact with the ball before any incidental arm contact occurs during rebounding.
Green (PHI) grabs and holds Smart's (BOS) left arm as Smart retrieves the rebound.
Smart (BOS) brings his off-hand towards Joe (PHI) on the perimeter, and marginal contact occurs with Joe's extended right arm.
Harris (PHI) reflexively places his arms around Freedom's (BOS) upper half and quickly releases as he moves around the screen.
Joe (PHI) brings his left arm toward Brown's (BOS) path and marginal contact occurs with Brown's front during the drive.
Brown (BOS) gathers the ball on his right foot and establishes his left foot as his pivot, which he maintains after he picks up his dribble.
Freedom (BOS) and Embiid (PHI) briefly engage and disengage off-ball in the post.
Curry (PHI) and Langford (BOS) briefly engage and disengage off-ball.
Harris (PHI) and Brown (BOS) briefly engage and disengage off-ball.
Harris (PHI) and Langford (BOS) come together at the same spot as they disengage following the pick.
Curry (PHI) brings his left arm toward Brown's (BOS) path and Brown moves through the marginal contact to continue on his path toward the basket.
Embiid (PHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he could be deemed to be imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Embiid (PHI) establishes verticality and absorbs the contact made with Brown (BOS) during the driving shot attempt.
Freedom (BOS) closes out the jump shot attempt and marginal body contact occurs with Embiid's (PHI) slightly extended right leg.
Green (PHI) is retreating alongside Tatum's (BOS) path and absorbs the marginal body contact before making clean contact with the ball. Any contact thereafter is deemed incidental.
Tatum (BOS) brings his off-arm toward Green's (PHI) front and marginal contact occurs as Tatum releases away from the contact.
Brown (BOS) is bracing for the contact from Curry (PHI) and marginal contact occurs as Brown releases away from the contact at the end of the drive.
Embiid (PHI) briefly grasps Freedom's (BOS) right arm during rebounding, and marginal contact occurs as Joe (PHI) deflects the ball away from Freedom.

Joe (PHI) is turning away from Smart (BOS) and absorbs the marginal body contact as Smart jumps toward him. Embiid (PHI) jumps vertically and is turning away from Smart when he absorbs the body contact made as Smart jumps toward him.
Embiid (PHI) initiates contact across Freedom's (BOS) right arm during his upward shooting motion.
Embiid (PHI) and Smart (BOS) come together after the release and incidental contact occurs as Smart's momentum is already causing him to fall to the floor.
Smart (BOS) swipes forward and brushes Curry's (PHI) front as marginal contact occurs in transition.
Smart (BOS) closes out the jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Embiid's (PHI) slightly extended right leg during the follow-through.
Green (PHI) cleanly steals the pass intended for Tatum (BOS).
After Green (PHI) loses control of the ball on his own, Tatum (BOS) brings his hands towards Green's upper body and marginal contact occurs as the ball goes out of bounds.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Green (PHI) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Boston.
Embiid (PHI) extends his hand forward into Freedom's (BOS) front and he does not remove his hand while Freedom is airborne during his jump shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) moves toward Green (PHI) after the release and marginal contact occurs with Green's back as he elevates for the potential rebound.
Brown (BOS) and Embiid (PHI) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Brown (BOS) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
Embiid (PHI) cleanly steals the pass intended for Brown (BOS).
Pritchard (BOS) commits a take foul on Embiid (PHI).
